arch:string.div: This project primarily provided zooarchaeological data. The project dataset did not include extensive description of contexts. Some contexts may have repeating properties, indicating that the context identifiers provided to Open Context were probably not unique. The Open Context editorial staff was unable to resolve these identifier issues. Therefore, these context descriptions should be seen as provisional.
